  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-08-08"
      class="main-meta">2010-08-08 14:55:43</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3519149_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  书尾几次提到“文革”和21世纪初的中国，作为国际关系专家，作者从外交关系和列强格局的角度分析义和团的起源，另辟蹊径，是分析中外关系的范例之作。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_3519149_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_3519149_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










